snippet.title: C64 Game - Judge Dredd
snippet.description:
Played with infinite stamina. This game doesn't have an ending but it's fun for a while. Instructions onscreen at the start.

Published: 1987, Melbourne House
Musician: Neil Brennan
Graphicians: Russel Comte & Greg Holland
Programmer: Doug Palmer
